Variable Declaration:

int mukiyam() {
    int variable_name = value;
}

Keyword for defining the main function: int mukiyam()
Keyword for variable declaration: int
Keyword for assignment: =

2. Conditional Statements:

haa (condition) {
    // True block
} uhh {
    // False block
}

Keyword for if statement: haa
Keyword for else statement: uhh

3. Loop Statements:

For Loop:

aku (initialization; condition; increment) {
    // Loop body
}

Keyword for for loop: aku

While Loop:

ohhh (condition) {
    // Loop body
}

Keyword for while loop: ohhh

Do-While Loop:

kick {
    // Loop body
} ohhh (condition);

Keyword for do-while loop: kick ohhh

4. Input/Output:

Paaru value;
sollu variable_name;

Keyword for output: Paaru
Keyword for input: sollu
